---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Home | Ela Sobol">
  <section style="padding: 5rem 2rem; background-color: #e3f2fd; border-bottom: 5px solid #fff;">
    <div style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
      
      <div style="flex: 2; min-width: 300px;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 3.5rem; color: #1565c0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Hi, I'm Ela Sobol</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #2c3e50;">
          I am a <strong>Data Science (AI track) and Psychology</strong> double-major at the <strong>College of William & Mary</strong>[cite: 4, 5]. 
          I am fascinated by the intersection of artificial intelligence and psychology. Specifically, I am interested in how we can use artificial intelligence tools 
          to maximize efficiency while preserving essential emotional and creative human elements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; justify-content: center;">
        <img src={`${base}/me.jpeg`} alt="Ela Sobol" style="width: 350px; height: 450px; border-radius: 20px; object-fit: cover; box-shadow: 20px 20px 0px #fff;" />
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
      <div style="background: #e8f5e9; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.1);">
        <h3 style="color: #2e7d32; margin-top: 0;">Research</h3>
        <p>As a <strong>Research Assistant at the DiGI Lab</strong>, I support faculty political psychology research through data collection and analysis[cite: 12, 13].</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="background: #e8f5e9; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.1);">
        <h3 style="color: #2e7d32; margin-top: 0;">Leadership</h3>
        <p>I lead the <strong>Pointe Blank Dance Company</strong> as President, overseeing a 70-member organization[cite: 21, 22].</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background: #e8f5e9; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.1);">
        <h3 style="color: #2e7d32; margin-top: 0;">Campus Presence</h3>
        <p>Working for <strong>Undergraduate Admissions</strong>, I represent William & Mary as a Campus Tour Guide[cite: 19].</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="margin: 2rem auto 5rem; padding: 3.5rem; background: #fff0f5; border-radius: 30px; max-width: 1000px; border: 1px solid rgba(194, 24, 91, 0.05);">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; color: #ad1457;">Outside of academics...</h2>
    
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4rem; justify-content: center;">
      
      <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px; text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: #ad1457;">The Outdoors</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          In my free time, I love dancing, camping, and hiking. I've already camped in two National Parks (<strong>Shenandoah and Acadia</strong>) and my dream is to visit as many as possible.
        </p>
        <img src={`${base}/shen.jpeg`} alt="Camping in Shenandoah" style="width: 100%; height: 450px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);" />
      </div>

      <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px; text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: #ad1457;">My cats!</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          At home, I have two cats that I love named <strong>Mercedes and Benz</strong>. They are such good companions, and I really enjoy spending time with them.
        </p>
        <img src={`${base}/cats.jpeg`} alt="Mercedes and Benz" style="width: 100%; height: 450px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);" />
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
